{"tid":2490850,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"下海有譜？爆大咖女星收天價片酬拍AV　本人突發震撼聲明","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:45:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"675c62de2a05c297079b6a906a64166afa5e8e7d","tid":2490850,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"日本知名成人片公司Soft On Demand（SOD）日前宣布砸下1億日圓（約台幣2628萬元），邀請大咖女星下海拍AV，聲稱是「史無前例的大Project」，消息曝光立刻引發網友瘋猜是哪位女星，其中以24歲辣模木村有希、22歲寫真女星小倉優香，以及「前國民女團的前成員」K小姐為熱門「候選人」，沒想到就在此時，小倉優香拋出震撼聲明，網友直喊「真的要下海拍AV了嗎？」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/22/2787409-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F22%2F2787409-PH.jpg&h=095ecb1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小倉優香被網友認為要下海拍AV。（ 圖／翻攝自小倉優香IG）<br />\n<br />\n小倉優香13日對外發出聲明，表示為了能夠更自由地發展，決定退出待了8年的經紀公司，並且會更換藝名，從原本的「小倉優香」變成「小倉ゆうか」，未來會帶著笑容繼續努力，雖然她的內文沒有寫下任何有關下海、SOD等字眼，但網友卻已經心裡「有譜」，「SOD重金請的知名女星，日本網友真的猜到了嗎」、「是她的話&hellip;超值得期待」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/22/2787411-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F22%2F2787411-PH.jpg&h=28386636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小倉優香巧合發聲明換經紀公司、改藝名。（圖／翻攝自小倉優香IG）<br />\n<br />\nSOD製作史上最大企劃，不僅願意支付高達1億日幣的天價片酬，製作費更是超過2億日幣（約台幣5256萬元），由於小倉優香身陷小三醜聞，就算有亮眼外型也接不到任何工作，一直讓網友覺得她會決定下海，如今巧合的宣布要換經紀公司，立刻引來網友猜測，不過也有人認為別想太多，應該只是純粹換公司，「只是改名而已」、「人家只是跳槽，不太可能拍AV」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/01/2695945-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F01%2F2695945-PH.jpg&h=cf2318eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲部分網友覺得，小倉優香是正常換公司，不需過度腦補。（圖／翻攝自小倉優香IG）"},{"pid":"d85168c32d7d880c5c7bee75152f1062b8926f01","tid":2490850,"uid":255310,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"專心返工啦腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43430645abafb13e0d8f59d77a638a84053a5ec9","tid":2490850,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"想做男優了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24853fd469dbb32b451ebd1daeee2c2aee659a0f","tid":2490850,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d85168c32d7d880c5c7bee75152f1062b8926f01","tid":2490850,"uid":255310,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:15:43.000Z","msg":"專心返工啦腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"未返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0866441366c6571c10dc8e204b6d4d42ae8ff31c","tid":2490850,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43430645abafb13e0d8f59d77a638a84053a5ec9","tid":2490850,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"想做男優了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:24:18.000Z","msg":"唔係咁易架葉師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5699846d1b99cfd65eb5be574d1b344fabea2fbb","tid":2490850,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0866441366c6571c10dc8e204b6d4d42ae8ff31c","tid":2490850,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"43430645abafb13e0d8f59d77a638a84053a5ec9","tid":2490850,"uid":261849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"想做男優了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.g